
===================================
📌 1. Finglish Version (Persian Latin Script)
===================================

📖 **Tashrih:**
    Dastoor `fc-pattern` baraye peyda kardan font-ha (fonts) ba توجه به pattern-ha (patterns) است.
    Shoma mitavanid مشخصات font-ha ra bar اساس name, style ya khososiat-haye digar search konid.

⚙️ **Gozine-ha:**
    🔹 `fc-pattern [file ya directory]`  --> 📁 File ya pooshe-haye XML font config ra check mikonad. agar address dade nashavad, az config-haye default estefade mikonad.
    🔹 `fc-pattern font` --> 🔤 Hameye font-haye nasb shode ra list mikonad.
    🔹 `fc-pattern : family=Arial` --> 🔎 Font-haye family "Arial" ra peyda mikonad.
    🔹 `fc-pattern : family=Arial:style=Bold` --> 🔎 Font-haye family "Arial" ke style "Bold" daran ra peyda mikonad.

🛠 **Mesal-ha:**

    $ fc-pattern : family=Tahoma

    🔹 List font-haye family Tahoma.

    $ fc-pattern /usr/share/fonts/truetype/arial.ttf : family=Arial

    🔹 Check mikonad ke aya file arial.ttf font-haye family Arial ra darad ya na.

✅ **Mesal sade:**

    $ fc-pattern : hinting=True

    🔹 List font-haye ke hinting enable ast.

===================================
📌 2. English Version
===================================

📖 **Description:**
    The `fc-pattern` command is used to find fonts based on patterns.
    You can search for font characteristics based on name, style, or other attributes.

⚙️ **Options:**
    🔹 `fc-pattern [file or directory]`  --> 📁 Checks XML font config files or directories. If no address is given, it uses default configurations.
    🔹 `fc-pattern font` --> 🔤 Lists all installed fonts.
    🔹 `fc-pattern : family=Arial` --> 🔎 Finds fonts with the family "Arial".
    🔹 `fc-pattern : family=Arial:style=Bold` --> 🔎 Finds fonts with the family "Arial" and style "Bold".

🛠 **Examples:**

    $ fc-pattern : family=Tahoma

    🔹 Lists fonts with the family Tahoma.

    $ fc-pattern /usr/share/fonts/truetype/arial.ttf : family=Arial

    🔹 Checks if the file arial.ttf contains fonts with the family Arial.

✅ **Simple Example:**

    $ fc-pattern : hinting=True

    🔹 Lists fonts where hinting is enabled.
